CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 19th November, 2001
28 Kartika, 1923 (S)
The undersigned is directed to state that with effect from the 18th
November, 2001 : -
Shri Jagmohan relinquished the charge of the offices of Minister of
Tourism and Minister of Statistics & Programme Implementation and
assumed the charge of the office of Minister of Tourism and Culture;
and
i)
Smt Maneka Gandhi relinquished the charge of the office of Minister
of State (Independent charge) of the Ministry of Culture and
assumed the charge of the office of Minister of State (Independent
charge) of the Ministry of Statistics & Programme Implementation.
ii)
(P.'Gopalakrishnan)
for Cabinet Secretary.
